news.go.com/US/back-future-part-ii-scored-2015-predictions/story?id=27946920|title=How 'Back to the Future: Part II' Scored on 2015 Predictions|publisher=ABC News|date=October 22, 2015|accessdate=April 21, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.today.com/money/back-future-part-ii-writer-talks-about-2015-predictions-1D80410566|title='Back to the Future Part II' writer Bob Gale talks 2015 predictions|first=Keith|last=Wagstaff|date=|work=today.com|accessdate=April 21, 2017}}</ref><!-- today interviews a writer for the film -->\n|-\n| ''[[Barb Wire (film)|Barb Wire]]''\n| Film\n| 1996\n| 2017\n| Predicts a second [[American Civil War]] in 2017.<ref name=\"ds7\">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/feature/a818169/2017-predicted-by-movies/|title=7 times the movies predicted what 2017 will be like|author=|date=January 4, 2017|work=digitalspy.com|accessdate=April 14, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"[[Battlefield (Doctor Who)|Battlefield]]\" (from ''[[Doctor Who]]'')\n| TV series episode\n| 1989\n| 1997\n| By 1997, the United Kingdom has a king.\n|-\n| ''[[Battlefield 2]]''\n|Video game\n|2005\n|2007\n|Depicts a war between the United States and China, with battles taking place on [[Wake Island]]. Several Middle Eastern states have joined together to form a superstate known as the \"Middle Eastern Coalition\".\n|-\n| ''[[Battlefield 3]]''\n|Video game\n|2011\n|2014\n| Takes place during the \"War of 2014\" in the Iran-Iraq area.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.christianpost.com/news/xbox-games-with-gold-september-2017-news-free-games-include-battlefield-3-and-forza-5-next-month-196894/|title=Xbox 'Games With Gold' September 2017 News: Free Games Include 'Battlefield 3' and 'Forza 5' Next Month|author=|date=|website=Christianpost.com|accessdate=December 9, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Battlefield 4]]''\n|Video game\n|2013\n|2020\n| Takes place during the fictional \"War of 2020\".\n|-\n| ''[[Battle for the Planet of the Apes]]''\n| Film\n| 1973\n|data-sort-value=\"2000\"|{{Ci